footer.description: Ekibiina kya Gnosis Deutschland tikirukukora sente, kiri kimwe aha bibiina bya Gnosis International, kikuruukirira aha byahandiikirwe bya Gnostic ebyashemeirwe V.M. Samael Aun Weor omu myaka ya 1950 na 1999.
